    パッケージ 説明
    org.sxb.http
    包含了客户端/服务器端的HTTP基本抽象类 用于Restful
    Contains a basic abstraction over client/server-side HTTP.
    org.sxb.http.converter
    Provides an HttpMessageConverter abstraction to convert between Java objects and HTTP input/output messages.
    org.sxb.http.converter.json
    实现了Jackson跟FastJson Json String to Object Object to Json String Provides an HttpMessageConverter implementations for handling JSON.
    org.sxb.http.converter.xml
    Provides an HttpMessageConverter implementations for handling XML.
    org.sxb.http.server
    Contains an abstraction over server-side HTTP.
